  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I have digitized my dog so we can go on walks forever and you can join us too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a short and peaceful walking simulator, inspired by real life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In This Game You Can: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Pet the dog! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566550/extras/867096c129db487962eb121a0b95a69c.poster.avif?t=1728506499\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566550/extras/867096c129db487962eb121a0b95a69c.webm?t=1728506499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566550/extras/867096c129db487962eb121a0b95a69c.mp4?t=1728506499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play fetch & tug of war with our dog</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566550/extras/4cede8f28bba4afa1e0efc8d860a9d8e.poster.avif?t=1728506499\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566550/extras/4cede8f28bba4afa1e0efc8d860a9d8e.webm?t=1728506499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566550/extras/4cede8f28bba4afa1e0efc8d860a9d8e.mp4?t=1728506499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover photos</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566550/extras/22f40